title: Lunchbox's Overnight Stay At The Murder House + Bobby Got A Speeding Ticket + Eddie's Jealous Of His Wife
itunes:title: Lunchbox's Overnight Stay At The Murder House + Bobby Got A Speeding Ticket + Eddie's Jealous Of His Wife
description:
Lunchbox spent the night at the Villisca Axe Murder House in Iowa. He called in with a report on what he experienced and if he thinks the house is actually haunted. Bobby got a speeding ticket for going 75 in a 55! Eddie is jealous because of something he noticed on his wife’s Instagram. Plus, Bobby talks to Donna who has a B-Teamer license plate!
